{4} \" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?\\frac{y}{2}-\\frac{3}{2}+8=\\frac{3y}{4}+\\frac{15}{4} \" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?\\frac{y}{2}-\\frac{3y}{4}=\\frac{15}{4}&plus;\\frac{3}{2}-8\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?\\frac{y}{2}-\\frac{3y}{4}=\\frac{15}{4}+\\frac{3}{2}-8\" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?\\frac{2y-3y}{4}=\\frac{15&plus;6-32}{4} \" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?\\frac{2y-3y}{4}=\\frac{15+6-32}{4} \" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?-y=-11\\rightarrow y=11\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?-y=-11\\rightarrow y=11\" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\\frac{1}{2}\\left ( \\left ( 11 \\right )-3 \\right ) &plus;3\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\\frac{1}{2}\\left ( \\left ( 11 \\right )-3 \\right ) +3\" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}y=4&plus;3=7\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}y=4+3=7\" /><br>Jawaban: B. 7', 'tiu', 43),
('628888e25c187', '628888e1c77ab', 'Andi memiliki 48 karung gula di tokonya dengan berat masing-masing sama. Andi kemudian mengirim 3/8 gulanya ke Toko Cibinong dan 2/5 ?gulanya ke Toko Cimahi. Jika yang masih tersedia adalah 1728 kg. Berapa berat setiap karung semula?', '628888e25c886', 'Misalkan <img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\" /> berat semula<br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x-\\frac{3}{8}x-\\frac{2}{5}x=1728\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x-\\frac{3}{8}x-\\frac{2}{5}x=1728\" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}\\frac{40-15-16}{40}x=1728\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}\\frac{40-15-16}{40}x=1728\" /><br><img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\\frac{1728\\times 40}{9}=7680\" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}x=\\frac{1728\\times 40}{9}=7680\" /><br>Berat setiap karung <img class=\"inline\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}=\\frac{7680}{48}=160 \" title=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.image?\\dpi{110}=\\frac{7680}{48}=160 \" /> kg<br>Jawaban: B. 160', 'tiu', 44),
('628888e25fd70', '628888e1c77ab', '250 pon + 6,75 ton + 36.000 ons + 15 kuintal + 1500 dag = ... kg.', '628888e260960', '250 Pon = 125 Kg<br>6,75 Ton = 6.750 kg<br>36.000 Ons = 3.600 kg<br>15 Kuintal = 1.500 Kg<br>1500 dag = 15 kg<br>Total = 11.990<br>Jawaban: A. 11.990', 'tiu', 45),
('628888e26416c', '628888e1c77ab', '3 gross + 13 lusin + 23 kodi + 330 buah =....', '628888e264a47', '1 gross = 144 buah, maka 3 x 144 = 432<br>1 lusin 12 buah, maka 13 x 12 = 156<br>1 kodi = 20 buah, maka 23 x 20 = 460<br>Jumlah = 432 + 156 + 460 + 330 = 1378<br>Jawaban: B. 1378', 'tiu', 46),
